DAY 16 Manual CRN Entry System

Today I removed the scanner feature. I implemented manual CRN entry with popup-based student data fetch. This made the system easier to use.

DAY 17 Daily Meal Entry Page

Today I created the daily meal entry page. Manager can enter breakfast, lunch, dinner, and extra meals. Quantity and price fields were added.

DAY 18 Meal Type Handling

Today I implemented proper meal type handling. I used JavaScript and PHP to manage different meal types. Data was stored correctly in the database.

DAY 19 Save Meal Entry Logic

Today I wrote backend logic to save meal entries. Meal data was inserted into student_meal_details table. Amount calculation was also implemented.

DAY 20 Extra Meal Handling

Today I added logic to handle extra meals separately. This ensured accurate billing for students.

DAY 21 Billing Module Development

Today I developed the billing module. Monthly bills are automatically calculated based on meal entries.

DAY 22 PDF Generation Integration

Today I integrated Dompdf library. I followed Dompdf documentation from GitHub. Billing PDFs were generated successfully.

DAY 23 Single Student Billing PDF

Today I created single student billing PDF. It shows meal details and total amount clearly.

DAY 24 Meal Type Bug Fix

Today I fixed a bug where meal type was showing incorrectly in PDF. I corrected backend query logic.

DAY 25 JavaScript Bug Fixes

Today I fixed JavaScript issues related to menu loading. I removed unnecessary parameters from fetch requests.

DAY 26 UI Improvements

Today I improved the user interface. I fixed spacing, buttons, and table alignment.

DAY 27 Security Enhancements

Today I added session checks on all important pages. Unauthorized access was restricted properly.

DAY 28 Testing with Dummy Data

